WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.157 --> 00:00:01.230
Hello Facebook Ads people!

00:00:01.230 --> 00:00:02.102
I'm Konstantinos 

00:00:02.102 --> 00:00:03.720
and today we're going to talk about

00:00:03.720 --> 00:00:06.240
avoiding the bans on the Facebook platform.

00:00:26.261 --> 00:00:28.450
Help me, help me, my account got banned!

00:00:28.450 --> 00:00:30.450
I don't know what happened!

00:00:30.646 --> 00:00:33.031
Help please, heeelp!

00:00:33.031 --> 00:00:36.799
I have done nothing wrong and my account got banned!

00:00:36.799 --> 00:00:38.268
Please, get me my account back.

00:00:38.268 --> 00:00:40.615
Please, get me my account back! Please!

00:00:40.615 --> 00:00:41.802
I need your help!

00:00:41.802 --> 00:00:43.520
Heeeelp!

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:44.185
STOP!

00:00:45.975 --> 00:00:47.274
Heeelp!

00:00:53.235 --> 00:00:55.020
I know. It is frustrating.

00:00:55.030 --> 00:00:55.826
Let me tell you 

00:00:55.826 --> 00:00:57.665
that 99% of the cases 

00:00:57.665 --> 00:00:58.738
it is not your fault

00:00:58.738 --> 00:01:00.540
and you will get your account back.

00:01:00.550 --> 00:01:02.651
There is only one simple, tiny rule

00:01:02.651 --> 00:01:03.535
that you have to follow.

00:01:03.742 --> 00:01:05.519
Keep it simple and be polite.

00:01:05.910 --> 00:01:07.380
Facebook customer support

00:01:07.380 --> 00:01:09.233
is not your typical customer support.

00:01:09.233 --> 00:01:10.110
Just to be clear.

00:01:10.120 --> 00:01:11.367
Even if you spend millions

00:01:11.367 --> 00:01:12.415
per month on the platform, 

00:01:12.816 --> 00:01:14.075
you are going to be treated like

00:01:14.075 --> 00:01:15.715
you spend $5 per month.

00:01:15.715 --> 00:01:18.541
Simply, because they don't give a fuck!

00:01:19.119 --> 00:01:20.835
Try to send a simple messenge saying 

00:01:20.835 --> 00:01:22.780
"Hello, I have done nothing wrong.

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:23.853
I want my account back."

00:01:24.077 --> 00:01:25.216
Nothing else.

00:01:25.577 --> 00:01:26.860
Don't go into details.

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:28.501
Maybe it was this or that 

00:01:28.501 --> 00:01:30.347
in order to avoid any misunderstandings.

00:01:30.631 --> 00:01:32.459
By the way, if you don't know

00:01:32.459 --> 00:01:34.433
where to appeal to get your account back

00:01:34.433 --> 00:01:36.052
either go to account quality

00:01:36.052 --> 00:01:38.390
from your menu in business manager or

00:01:38.390 --> 00:01:40.060
in the error meson that is going to

00:01:40.070 --> 00:01:41.920
appear in the ads manager

00:01:41.930 --> 00:01:43.660
you should be able to see the review button.

00:01:44.390 --> 00:01:46.330
Most probably, you are watching this video

00:01:46.330 --> 00:01:48.129
after you have asked for a review

00:01:48.129 --> 00:01:49.920
and you are just waiting for an answer.

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:51.900
Just keep it simple from now on.

00:01:51.910 --> 00:01:53.499
If you haven't done it so far

00:01:53.499 --> 00:01:55.395
and be sure to watch the whole video

00:01:55.395 --> 00:01:56.438
because this is just

00:01:56.438 --> 00:01:57.900
the beginning of all the things

00:01:57.910 --> 00:01:58.988
you need to know about

00:01:58.988 --> 00:02:00.301
this unpleasant situation.

00:02:00.604 --> 00:02:01.713
Most of the times,

00:02:01.713 --> 00:02:03.531
they might ask you your ID 

00:02:03.531 --> 00:02:05.502
to identify who you are and this is one

00:02:05.502 --> 00:02:07.205
of the most common reasons to get flagged.

00:02:07.693 --> 00:02:10.000
Other common reasons are the two factor authenticator

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.140
 and having an unverified business.

00:02:12.554 --> 00:02:14.920
And now the 1 million dollar question.

00:02:14.930 --> 00:02:16.522
If I do all of these,

00:02:16.522 --> 00:02:17.930
is there still a possibility 

00:02:17.930 --> 00:02:20.740
that my account is going to get banned?

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:22.359
Let's play the drums...

00:02:23.812 --> 00:02:25.095
and the answer is 

00:02:25.726 --> 00:02:26.555
"Hell Yes!"

00:02:26.555 --> 00:02:28.260
Of course you might be banned.

00:02:28.290 --> 00:02:30.785
Sometimes the bans are completely random

00:02:30.785 --> 00:02:32.012
and they have nothing

00:02:32.012 --> 00:02:33.840
to do with any of your actions.

00:02:34.147 --> 00:02:35.089
Just be patient, 

00:02:35.089 --> 00:02:37.468
after you have submitted the review and wait.

00:02:37.580 --> 00:02:39.000
Sometimes it takes 10 minutes,

00:02:39.010 --> 00:02:40.890
sometimes it can take up to 5 days

00:02:40.890 --> 00:02:42.986
if you're unfortunate enough to get banned

00:02:42.986 --> 00:02:44.076
on a Friday night, 

00:02:44.076 --> 00:02:46.496
which will also ruin your weekend by the way,

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:48.740
you can thank Facebook for that.

00:02:55.406 --> 00:02:56.654
Another note is that 

00:02:56.654 --> 00:02:58.654
if you get banned, for example, in October

00:02:58.740 --> 00:03:00.667
and you ask for review 2 months later

00:03:00.667 --> 00:03:01.838
or even 5 months later,

00:03:02.077 --> 00:03:04.757
sorry, but most probably your account is gone

00:03:04.757 --> 00:03:06.472
and this is the point 

00:03:06.472 --> 00:03:08.560
where all your problems are going to start.

00:03:08.851 --> 00:03:11.133
So if your account ever gets banned,

00:03:11.133 --> 00:03:11.970
act fast!

00:03:12.133 --> 00:03:13.176
Don't neglect it!

00:03:13.654 --> 00:03:15.555
Even if you don't plan on advertising

00:03:15.555 --> 00:03:16.528
for the next months.

00:03:16.947 --> 00:03:19.250
Facebook doesn't ban account but people.

00:03:19.430 --> 00:03:20.960
If you get a permanent ban

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:22.745
for selling CBD products, for instance,

00:03:23.058 --> 00:03:24.537
or having a bad page rating

00:03:24.537 --> 00:03:25.652
or even by mistake,

00:03:26.002 --> 00:03:27.895
it is exactly the same for them,

00:03:27.895 --> 00:03:29.500
and when they say that

00:03:29.500 --> 00:03:30.600
their decision is final,

00:03:30.673 --> 00:03:31.970
they actually mean it.

00:03:32.257 --> 00:03:34.040
And what does a fresh start mean?

00:03:34.530 --> 00:03:37.929
New pixel, new high cost per acquisition, 

00:03:37.929 --> 00:03:39.310
new gathering of data.

00:03:39.340 --> 00:03:40.956
And the saddest part is that

00:03:40.956 --> 00:03:43.299
in most cases it's not even your fault.

00:03:45.530 --> 00:03:47.697
My suggestion after seeing businesses

00:03:47.697 --> 00:03:50.852
