00:10:04.140 --> 00:10:05.705
But if you haven't

00:10:05.705 --> 00:10:07.566
1. Don't panic.

00:10:07.782 --> 00:10:10.966
2. Request a review and keep it polite and simple.

00:10:11.210 --> 00:10:13.510
3. Have a backup plan with several

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:15.490
ad accounts within the same business.

00:10:15.856 --> 00:10:16.583
In any case, 

00:10:16.583 --> 00:10:17.695
